      <title>债券利差能降到多低？五个值得关注的数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-04/bond-spreads-continue-to-tighten-how-low-can-they-go-five-numbers-to-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[公司债券估值已达到令人咋舌的水平，随着养老基金经理和保险公司的资金涌入加剧资产竞争，公司债券估值发出了近 30 年来最大的警告。到目前为止，投资者对风险持乐观态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-04/bond-spreads-continue-to-tighten-how-low-can-they-go-five-numbers-to-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Jan 2025 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
